        <div id="tribute-info">
            A Chesterfield FC supporters' podcast with a bit of humour and a great array of features and quizzes. It's presented by Demetri and Euan of the Manchester Spireites and is usually released on Tuesdays...
        </div>
        <a id="tribute-link" href="https://linktr.ee/QuigleyTuesdays" target="_blank">Listen to Quigley Tuesdays</a>

        <section id="features">
            <h2>Podcast Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Favourite player who wore the number of the current episode.</li>
                <li>Real Football Talk - actual chat about the football that's happened recently</li>
                <li>Bonkers Bob’s Board Comment of the Week - what daft things are fellow fans saying online?</li>
                <li>Blues in the News - any current or former Chesterfield personnel in the news</li>
                <li>Villainous Victorians - Euan must guess whether these names are real Chesterfield players from the past or made up by Demetri</li>
                <li>Official Club Input - occasionally the club has something to say on the pod!</li>
                <li>Paul Cook, Starmer, Saunders, Gnanduillet, Mandeville - these guys have been known to feature</li>
                <li>Dean Saunders Quiz - sometimes Dean comes on to grill Euan on his Spireites knowledge</li>
                <li>Dolphin Drainage and Plumbing have a complimentary sponsorship deal with the podcast</li>
                <li>Quigley’s Kangaroo Court - any sweeping changes that you would like to change in football?</li>
                <li>Misheard Song Lyrics - Peter Kay likes this one</li>
                <li>Oops He Did It Again - new song ideas for the Kop Choir!</li>
                <li>Hot Crossley’s Buns - Big Norm has tiktok and uses it with great gastronomic intent</li>
                <li>Quiz: Name the Match from the Order of Goalscorers</li>
                <li>The Chain - build an XI based on a rule, linked by one player in the previous XI</li>
                <li>Spireites Hatred Index Treatise</li>
                <li>Whelan Fortuné - Euan spins a wheel containing every CFC player to play for the club since 2003 and Demetri must guess who it is from Euan's clues. Quigley Tuesdays then tries to build a best XI from all the Whelan Fortunés.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>


